lazard group llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Lazard Group LLC provides financial advisory and asset management. The Company offers provides advice on mergers and acquisitions, strategic matters, restructuring and capital structure, capital raising ,and corporate finance to corporations, partnerships, institutions, government and individuals. Lazard Group serves customers worldwide.




