IT Budget




Lazard Limited is an international financial advisory and asset management firm that crafts solutions to the financial and strategic challenges of the clients. Lazard Limited, which is incorporated under the laws of Bermuda, has a controlling interest in Lazard Group,… MoreLazard Limited is an international financial advisory and asset management firm that crafts solutions to the financial and strategic challenges of the clients. Lazard Limited, which is incorporated under the laws of Bermuda, has a controlling interest in Lazard Group, LLC, a Delaware limited liability company, and one of the world's largest investment banks. Lazard Asset Management LLC (LAM) is an indirect subsidiary of Lazard Ltd.
IT Priorities:
•Provide support to employees involved in various banking practices.

IT Structure
•The IT department supports the company through technical support for investment banking, financial/HR applications, enterprise computer, banking applications, corporate applications, database infrastructure, desktop engineering, SharePoint applications, the help desk ,… MoreIT Priorities:
•Provide support to employees involved in various banking practices.

IT Structure
•The IT department supports the company through technical support for investment banking, financial/HR applications, enterprise computer, banking applications, corporate applications, database infrastructure, desktop engineering, SharePoint applications, the help desk , and global technology.

IT Vendors:
•The company outsourced its back-office operations to Citigroup's global Transaction Services.
•Also appointed State Street Corporation to provide range of investment operations outsourcing services.
•Under the outsourcing agreement, 70 of the company's employees were to transfer to State Street.

IT Intelligence Snippets

2013
•IT staff members use IBM and Micrsofot operating systems, as well as IBM and thomson applications.





