Asset Management
Financial Advisory






















An advisory practice tailored to serve the unique needs of mid-sized companies








Middle Market Advisory

Lazard Middle Market's advisory practice is tailored to serving the unique needs of mid-sized companies, while delivering the sophisticated services, global perspective and broad resources of Lazard. We are distinguished by the following key factors:Deep Sector Expertise. Our senior bankers are national leaders in specific industry segments, bringing knowledge of sector dynamics and key participants.Global Access to Decision Makers. Lazard’s long-term relationships with CEOs, board members and sponsors on a worldwide basis provide unparalleled buyer access and strategic insight for our middle market clients.Transaction Craftsmanship, Trusted Advice. Our sophisticated professionals combine the highest level of transaction leadership with astute judgment to provide customized, analytically robust solutions.
 
 





Our Services:




M&A and Strategic Advisory





Corporate Finance Advisory





Restructuring





Financial Sponsors Group







